  "source": "refund-policy.txt",
  "text": "Refund Policy\r\n\r\nThe academy offers a limited refund policy for active subscriptions.\r\n\r\nRefund requests must be submitted in writing through email or the academy support desk.\r\n\r\nRefund eligibility is determined based on the number of classes attended under the subscription.\r\n\r\nRefund Schedule\r\n\r\n- If a refund is requested after attending 1 class, 100% of the subscription amount is refundable.\r\n- If a refund is requested after attending 2 classes, 85% of the subscription amount is refundable.\r\n- If a refund is requested after attending 3 classes, 75% of the subscription amount is refundable.\r\n- After the first 3 classes, refunds are calculated on a prorated basis based on unused classes.\r\n\r\nMaximum Refund Limit\r\n\r\nRegardless of the number of unused classes remaining, the refund amount after the first 3 attended classes shall never exceed 50% of the original subscription value.\r\n\r\nNon-Refundable Charges\r\n\r\nRegistration fees, admission fees, assessment fees, and third-party payment gateway charges are non-refundable.\r\n\r\nLoan-Funded Subscriptions\r\n\r\nSubscriptions that have been paid through an academy-approved loan program are not eligible for refunds under any circumstances.\r\n\r\nRefund Processing\r\n\r\nApproved refunds are generally processed within 7 to 14 business days and are returned to the original payment method whenever possible.\r\n\r\nThe academy reserves the right to request additional information before approving a refund.",
